data.description: WOW, stunningly beautiful home ready for you! This house offers Luxury living while just minutes from Downtown. This beauty features over 3200 square feet of living space with exquisite design. Open floor plan with 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and hardwood floors throughout. This house was completely remodeled in 2022 so NEW everything inside. The kitchen has a quartz massive island, stainless steel appliances, and modern fixtures. The spacious living room has a modern fireplace. The master suite has a beautiful bathroom with a stand alone tub and huge separate shower, with a walk-in closet. 2 car garage. Fenced backyard. One of Garfield Ridge's finest. Come fall in love with the HOME.
